OL,6,     FArgentina v Algeria (Kick-off
OL,7,     F2.00am). Laura Woods presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group J match at
OL,9,     FKansas City Stadium in the USA, as
OL,10,     Fthe reigning champions play their
OL,11,     Ffirst game in defence of their
OL,12,     Ftitle. The South Americans beat
OL,13,     FFrance on penalties in the 2022
OL,14,     Ffinal after the game had ended 3-3
OL,15,     Fafter extra-time in one of the
OL,16,     Fmost thrilling finals of all time,
OL,17,     Fwith France's Kylian Mbappe
OL,18,     Fscoring only the second ever
OL,19,     Fhat-trick in a World Cup final.
OL,20,     FThat was Argentina's third success
OL,21,     Fat this tournament after victories
OL,22,     Fin 1978 and 1986. They will be
